@node "Table" "Table of spelled out Chords"

Table of all the used chord spelled out in intervals.
------------------------------------------------------

 Maj   -  1 ,  3 ,  5
 min   -  1 , b3 ,  5
 dim   -  1 , b3 , b5
 aug   -  1 ,  3 , #5
 sus4  -  1 ,  4 ,  5
 Maj7  -  1 ,  3 ,  5 ,  7
 min7  -  1 , b3 ,  5 , b7
 x7    -  1 ,  3 ,  5 , b7           (also known as dominant 7)
 ř7    -  1 , b3 , b5 , b7           (also known as ř or half-diminished 7)
 o7    -  1 , b3 , b5 , bb7 or 6     (also known as diminished 7)
 +7    -  1 ,  3 , #5 ,  7           (also known as augmented 7 or #5/7)
 mM7   -  1 , b3 ,  5 ,  7           (pronounced as minorMajor7)
 s4M7  -  1 ,  4 ,  5 ,  7           (pronounced as sus4Major7)
 s4m7  -  1 ,  4 ,  5 , b7           (pronounced as sus4minor7)

@endnode

